  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1703513053\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/fc8079ff6696e8fa4f4a070a63ca432a.avif?t=1703513053\" width=616 height=170 /></span><br><br>Memory Traces:Egypt. <strong> is a 3D puzzle game </strong><br>where the player needs to <strong>repair destroyed artifacts.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/617a710c42a9410214213e39dc86ef75.avif?t=1703513053\" width=616 height=170 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/32a74c77c658e968f6d8f12c01212681.poster.avif?t=1703513053\" width=616 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/32a74c77c658e968f6d8f12c01212681.webm?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/32a74c77c658e968f6d8f12c01212681.mp4?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/6319ce183a4f66709a4db17619f700bf.avif?t=1703513053\" width=616 height=170 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Now you don't have to wait for the piece to come back to pick up another piece.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/e797f0c379eff0256473575d618e87ae.poster.avif?t=1703513053\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/e797f0c379eff0256473575d618e87ae.webm?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/e797f0c379eff0256473575d618e87ae.mp4?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You can now rotate and hold a part while finding the correct angle.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/349667721cef69a68e215e6f66054fc4.poster.avif?t=1703513053\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/349667721cef69a68e215e6f66054fc4.webm?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/349667721cef69a68e215e6f66054fc4.mp4?t=1703513053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Now you can rotate using the keys: A left and D right.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150580/extras/29ea2765f22224988b57621461373f0a.poster.avif?t=1703513053\" wid