ession, <strong>San is taken to his second place from his past: Egypt.</strong><br>The fragmented artifacts represent your lost memories and<br>each artifact you repair is a restored memory trace of San.<br><br>- Who is San?<br><strong>- You don't remember?! You are San!</strong><br><br><br><strong>Are you able</strong> to repair all artifacts?!<br><br>Will you be able to <strong>recover all your memories?</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>------ Come be Part of our Community and Follow the News ------ </strong></h2><strong>In the Discord community you can follow the development of the project:</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> news<br></li><li> leave feedback <br></li><li> much more</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > In-game content </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3 <strong>Beautiful Sceneries</strong> Inspired by Egypt<br></li><li> 3 Phases<br></li><li> 25 Levels<br></li><li>  Pitchers, Statues, Sarcophagus and more<br></li><li>  <strong>25 Artifacts to Restore</strong><br></li><li>  + 1000 <strong>Pieces to assemble the Puzzles</strong></li></ul>",
